@* this will also be used as page title in main layout *@
@{ ViewData["title"] = "Unhandled exception was caught in controller action."; }

@* content header *@
<div class="main-content-header">
	<span class="title">@ViewData["title"]</span>
</div>

@* content itself *@
<div class="p-3">
    <p>This page exists, so that you can still see queries executed before the exception, in the browser console.</p>
    <p>Use a debugger to inspect the exception, your IDE should have paused on it.</p>
    <p>If exception was thrown due to query, you can inspect the query SQL in result of <i>var sql = RecordCommandSql(dbCmd);</i> inside the corresponding query method of <i>Sql</i> class.</p>
</div>